title: Ep. - 280 - JANE WIEDLIN FROM THE GO-GOS YUMMY MUMMIES
description:
Jane Wiedlin from Showtime’s documentary on The Go-Gos, which chronicles the meteoric rise to fame of a band born of the LA punk scene that not only captured but created a zeitgeist.

 

Author and toddler sleep expert Megan Pierson helps Kate review Yummy Mummies on Netflix, an Australian reality tv show which follows wealthy, expectant mums who support each other through the challenges of pregnancy and motherhood.
